pends on scope — number of filming days, locations and deliverables. Viven builds packages from single-day shoots to multi-day content libraries like this one. Request a quote and you'll receive timing and a clear offer within 48 hours."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Can Viven produce large content libraries for other companies?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes — the same batch-production model (many videos and photos captured in few, well-planned days) works for any organisation that needs 12+ months of content. Viven has produced for UBS, Porsche, ON, FIFA and Philips."}}]}]};
---
<Base lang={lang} slug={slug} active="projects" singleLang={true} langUrls={{"en":"/en/case-study-how-viven-helped-siemens-switzerland-amplify-their-employer-branding/","de":"/de/case-study-wie-viven-siemens-schweiz-dabei-half-sein-employer-branding-zu-staerken/","es":"/es/caso-de-exito-como-viven-ayudo-a-siemens-a-ampliar-su-marca-de-empleador/"}} title={title} description={description}>
